### ============================================
### 06 — 订阅通知接口
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

# ------------------------------------------
# 6.1 订阅到票提醒
# ------------------------------------------
### 用户1订阅兵马俑到票提醒
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/subscribe?voucherId=1001&userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 用户2订阅故宫到票提醒
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/subscribe?voucherId=1002&userId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 用户3订阅九寨沟到票提醒
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/subscribe?voucherId=1003&userId=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 用户1再次订阅同一景区（测试幂等性）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/subscribe?voucherId=1001&userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ------------------------------------------
# 6.2 查询排队位置
# ------------------------------------------
### 查询用户1在兵马俑的排队位置
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/position?voucherId=1001&userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 查询用户2在故宫的排队位置
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/position?voucherId=1002&userId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 查询未订阅用户的排队位置（期望返回未订阅）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/position?voucherId=1001&userId=9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ------------------------------------------
# 6.3 取消订阅
# ------------------------------------------
### 用户1取消兵马俑订阅
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/subscribe?voucherId=1001&userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 取消后再查询位置（期望返回未订阅）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/position?voucherId=1001&userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 重新订阅（取消后可再次订阅）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify/subscribe?voucherId=1001&userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
